# ─── OPTIONAL API KEYS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# All keys below are optional and FREE to obtain.
# Tools work without them but will return instructions on how to register.

# opentransportdata.swiss — GTFS real-time feeds (trip updates, vehicle positions, alerts)
# Register free at: https://api-manager.opentransportdata.swiss/
OTD_API_KEY=

# ZEFIX — Swiss Commercial Register REST API
# Register free at: https://www.zefix.admin.ch
ZEFIX_USER=
ZEFIX_PASS=

# FoodRepo (EPFL) — Swiss barcoded food products database
# Register free at: https://www.foodrepo.org/en/users/sign_up
FOODREPO_API_KEY=

# ─── NO KEY REQUIRED ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The following APIs work with zero configuration:
#   - transport.opendata.ch  (trains, buses, trams)
#   - GeoAdmin / swisstopo   (geocoding, elevation, coordinates, maps)
#   - opendata.swiss CKAN    (14,000+ official Swiss datasets)
#   - OpenParlData           (parliamentary data)
#   - Fedlex                 (federal law SPARQL)
#   - MeteoSwiss OGD         (weather datasets)
#   - BAFU Hydrodaten        (river levels, floods)
#   - OpenPLZ                (postal codes, streets)
#   - SNB / BFS              (statistics, finance)
#   - SEM                    (migration data)
